          <h1 class="pb-4 m-3 text-center">Spanish Wills & Testament Services - Protect Your Assets</h1>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <p>Creating a Spanish will is essential for anyone owning property or assets in Spain, ensuring your wishes are respected and your loved ones are protected. At <%= link_to "Roper Lawyers", "https://roperlawyers.com" %>, we are specialist Spanish will and testament lawyers with over 14 years of experience helping British and Irish clients secure their Spanish assets through proper estate planning. Our English-speaking team provides expert guidance on Spanish succession law, international will coordination, and comprehensive estate planning to protect your family's future.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <%= render 'main_page_sections/reviews', locals: { reviews: @reviews } %>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container px-4 py-5">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
          <h2 class="pb-4 m-3 text-center">Why You Need a Spanish Will</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-12">
          <p>Spanish succession law differs significantly from UK law, and without a Spanish will, your Spanish assets may not be distributed according to your wishes. Spanish forced heirship rules can override your UK will for Spanish assets, potentially leaving your spouse or chosen beneficiaries with less than intended. A properly drafted Spanish will ensures your Spanish property and assets are distributed according to your wishes while complying with Spanish law.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-12">
          <p>Having a Spanish will also significantly speeds up the inheritance process, reducing bureaucracy, legal costs, and stress for your beneficiaries. Without a Spanish will, your family may face lengthy and expensive probate proceedings in Spain, potentially taking years to resolve. Our expert will services ensure your Spanish assets are protected and your family's inheritance process is as smooth as possible.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-light">
    <div class="container px-4 py-5">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
          <h2 class="pb-4 m-3 text-center">Our Spanish Will Services</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 col-12 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Spanish Will Drafting</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Expert drafting of Spanish wills that comply with Spanish succession law while maximizing protection for your chosen beneficiaries.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-12 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">International Will Coordination</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Coordination between your Spanish and UK wills to ensure consistency and avoid conflicts in asset distribution across jurisdictions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-12 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Succession Law Advice</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Expert guidance on Spanish succession law, forced heirship rules, and strategies to protect your spouse and chosen beneficiaries.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 col-12 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Will Registration</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Professional registration of your Spanish will with the Spanish Central Will Registry to ensure it can be easily located when needed.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-12 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
